{"tid":451174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"My Central一買即撻蝕300萬","createTime":"2017-10-29T02:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T08:01:23.000Z","uid":65328,"like":9,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8d0123b5af0d9b25220bfe4a5ba04eb5c46195","tid":451174,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T02:18:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20171029&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20197824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171029%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20197824&d=Itfvph%2BQOrl1vKl0YnMCVAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=094e481a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171029%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20197824&h=34ef4ebc\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20171029&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20197824</a><br />\n<br />\n一名80後年輕女買家，日前動用近5,800萬元購入上環豪宅My Central兩個單位，最終撻定離場，短短一周損失近300萬元<br />\n<br />\n她今次豪擲近5,800萬元買上環豪宅，有指獲其老爺奶奶資助首期入市。<br />\n<br />\n該80後新抱為港人，其丈夫連夫家全為內地人。"},{"pid":"45baa5bd8e9d561b8548d9cd11e5793f2dc988a4","tid":451174,"uid":3302,"like":43,"dislike":6,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T02:19:33.000Z","msg":"港女真係雞黎"},{"pid":"b083f4bd958b6bd3a823411a38f12f9b471ce648","tid":451174,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T02:20:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港女真係雞黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f982c64d0a645a0ea249512f4da9fe4cc80616f","tid":451174,"uid":70205,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T02:20:59.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大陸佬又買港樓"},{"pid":"cdc13e602bebceec7a26e6a1eeaa99c874c2264f","tid":451174,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T02:24:16.000Z","msg":"地產見財化水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png